---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Disclaimer">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 32px;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p>Last updated: June 26, 2026 · Please read this section carefully before using the site.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px;">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>1. For technical and informational purposes only</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>AI Agents Hub</strong> is an independently maintained directory of AI agents,
          built for developers and researchers. All content on this site — including but not limited to
          articles, listings, comments, screenshots, links, and ratings — is provided
          <strong>for technical learning and informational purposes only</strong> and does not constitute
          investment, legal, tax, medical, or other professional advice.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Not affiliated, not an endorsement</h2>
        <p>
          This site is an <strong>independent third-party project</strong>. It is not affiliated with,
          endorsed by, sponsored by, or in partnership with any of the companies, operators, or investors
          behind the agents listed here. All product names, trademarks, logos, and brand assets remain the
          property of their respective owners; they are used on this site for identification and
          reference only.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any "Featured" label reflects <strong>unpaid editorial opinion</strong> based on publicly
          available information and the editor's subjective judgment. If a listing is ever sponsored,
          it will be clearly disclosed on the listing itself.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Accuracy and "as-is" provision</h2>
        <p>
          We do our best to keep information (versions, pricing, features, star counts, etc.) aligned
          with official sources, but the AI industry moves fast: a single agent's features, pricing, or
          license can change within weeks. The site is provided on an <strong>"AS IS" basis</strong> with
          <strong>no warranty of absolute accuracy, completeness, timeliness, or fitness for any purpose</strong>.
          Before making any decision — especially a paid decision or a production deployment — please
          <strong>verify against the agent's official site</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Third-party links and services</h2>
        <p>
          This site links out to third-party websites, GitHub repositories, download pages, sign-up
          pages, and authenticated app interfaces. The content, policies, availability, and security of
          those services are the responsibility of their respective operators. <strong>This site is not
          responsible for their behavior.</strong> When you leave this site, please read and follow the
          third party's own terms and privacy policy.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, the author, contributors, and host of this
          site <strong>shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential
          damages</strong> arising from the use of, or inability to use, the site's content — including
          but not limited to data loss, business interruption, lost opportunity, or lost profits.
        </p>
        <p>
          Please use this site only <strong>within the bounds of applicable law</strong>. Do not use it
          for activities that violate local laws, and do not use it as a tool or instructional material
          for unlawful behavior.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Changes and discontinuation</h2>
        <p>
          We may <strong>modify, suspend, or take down</strong> pages, listings, layouts, or this
          disclaimer at any time, without prior notice. Material changes will be recorded in the
          repository's <code>CHANGELOG</code>; you are welcome to follow along via PRs or issues.
        </p>

        <div class="verdict-box" style="margin-top: 32px;">
          <div class="label">TL;DR</div>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text);">
            <strong>For technical exchange and information only. Use within the bounds of the law. Any
            business or legal decision should rely on the official source.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
